  <name>PDFedit</name>
  <summary>PDF editor with ability to browse/edit the tree of raw pdf objects</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Free editor for PDF documents. Complete editing of PDF documents is possible with PDFedit.</p>
    <p>You can either change raw pdf objects (for advanced users) or use predefined gui functions.</p>
    <p> ---------- DISCLAIMER ---------- </p>
    <p>This is legacy software which uses old unmaintained libraries (Qt3, Xpdf 3.02) for which there are no security backports,</p>
    <p>therefore you should NOT open any untrusted pdf files with this software.</p>
  </description>
  <provides>
    <binary>pdfedit</binary>
  </provides>
